  "raw_answer": "解:∵AB⊥OP,∴AM=BM=\\frac{1}{2}AB=\\frac{1}{2}×4=2,在Rt△AOM中,OA=√{OA^{2}+AM^{2}}=√{1^{2}+2^{2}}=√{5},∵PA切⊙O于点A,∴OA⊥PA,∴∠OAP=90°,即∠PAM+∠OAM=90°,而∠PAM+∠P=90°,∴∠P=∠OAM,∴Rt△PAM∽Rt△AOM,∴\\frac{PA}{OA}=\\frac{AM}{OM},即\\frac{PA}{√{5}}=\\frac{2}{1},∴PA=2√{5}．故选:C．"
